(43, 17, 14, 43, 15, 18, 21, 'not of the world', 'Connection of World and Hatred', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of hatred from the world towards those who follow Christ. They highlight that believers are not of the world, which leads to persecution, as seen in the connection between being ''not of the world'' and the world''s hatred.', 'theme', 0.40499999999999997, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
