(43, 17, 15, 62, 5, 18, 18, 'keep them from the evil', 'Protection from Evil', 'This connection highlights the theme of divine protection from evil. Both passages emphasize being kept safe from the wicked one, illustrating a shared focus on God''s safeguarding of believers.', 'theme', 0.44699999999999995, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
