(43, 17, 15, 48, 1, 4, 4, 'keep them from the evil', 'Protection from Evil', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of being kept from evil. John 17:15 speaks of being protected from evil, while Galatians 1:4 mentions deliverance from this present evil world.', 'theme', 0.391, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(43, 17, 15, 42, 11, 4, 4, NULL, 'Protection from Evil', 'Both passages emphasize a plea for protection from evil and temptation. John 17:15 asks for keeping from evil, while Luke 11:4 requests deliverance from evil.', 'theme', 0.384, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
